    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. It feels like the deeper you go, the more these trees just start to look like a chaotic web of connections. Is there a specific way to keep track of all the different branches and sub-branches when the sentence gets really long, or is it just something you have to memorize/get used to seeing?",
